text: Akkineni Naga Chaitanya is an Indian actor who mainly appears in Telugu- language films. He made his career debut with Josh (2009), and his breakthrough came with Maaya Chesave (2010). He has established himself as one of the leading actors in Telugu cinema. He is son of actor Akkineni Nagarjuna and Lakshmi Daggubati and a paternal half-brother of actor Akhil Akkineni. He has received critical acclaim and success for his leading role in Premam (2016), Rarandoi Veduka Chudham (2017), Majili (2019), Venky Mama (2019) and Love Story (2021). == Sources == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Indian movie actors
title: Naga Chaitanya
